{"tid":1607354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣戰2.0】仲玩膠扮可憐？成個文宣戰俾你搞彎左喇！","createTime":"2019-09-30T20:40:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T00:10:53.000Z","uid":290390,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"becdc909744f7760fbb0482b4cf44a6c2e26712e","tid":1607354,"uid":290390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:40:14.000Z","msg":"Sharon Hom 呼籲香港人勿再以受害者身份出現，否則只會得到同情，但失去國際支持。呢句話我一直記住<br />\n<br />\n連儂牆不少文宣太著重突顯自己好慘，死了人，傷了幾多手足挨左幾多發彈等等。稍有變化就是惡搞，搞下insider jokes，心態仍然是社運模式，日久民眾就會看不懂連儂牆，或者看完只感到無事可作<br />\n<br />\n我們很少作有系統<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vXyd9Be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvXyd9Be.jpg&h=b1fdda44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2aLcFHV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2aLcFHV.jpg&h=559b11eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NM4dp9B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNM4dp9B.jpg&h=cd7c393c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n動員，以及宣揚反擊，這些是戰爭時的文宣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">參考二戰文宣，有幾個方向可以考慮：</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 呼籲民眾「參軍」、當救護或者以特定方式支援戰線<br />\n<br />\n2. 呼籲民眾集資，也就是美國隊長第一集，隊長前半部戲做的事情 (得，射俾612慘過射落海，明)<br />\n<br />\n3. 燃起民眾鬥志，宣揚甚至放大戰果，並突顯敵我矛盾<br />\n<br />\n4. 引入核心訊息「香港國難，需要你救國於危」<br />\n<br />\n切記，<span style=\"color: red;\">你的文宣只得1秒時間</span>，路人最多只會花1~1.5秒看完一句標題，如果圖文緊扣，時間或會加長少少，但係1秒就是多數人看大部份文宣的時間，絕對要撚字，撚走多餘字，簡單易明<br />\n<br />\n香港現在係全球抗<span style=\"color: red;\">[size=5]赤納粹[/size]</span>最前線，各位文宣戰同道，謹願文武並濟，志堅不屈<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"d0176075745cca56c1c44993fb95dbefbb714e77","tid":1607354,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:42:20.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n正面宣傳好有用"},{"pid":"e2c5df0a5d12f6885996a37e10908ec421bf6dbc","tid":1607354,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:42:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"15fc255dad9ccc4f811d96062dbff5efaa87a5e8","tid":1607354,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:43:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fabea328b1f69f6562447f8f548db232c9ae8be","tid":1607354,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:43:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7d09840dc2012b9f240ea8cfc683441025728a87","tid":1607354,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:43:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5782c89cba312a63e2f452c82a5674a3cc42cbdd","tid":1607354,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:43:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"49ce3a2e9067796386b27200f565c5f1f3718cb1","tid":1607354,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:43:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"468528bd06dcb47e973203d0995374e076117545","tid":1607354,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:43:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c94070f97e56fda785f84c727297ce0723255301","tid":1607354,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:43:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6ed2c3a1f3985c578831e31c362e753189b9f2b","tid":1607354,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:43:50.000Z","msg":"叫人加入連儂牆都可以"},{"pid":"cef3a5a84ecb8a7866fa88b303d7ee2cf9cc636f","tid":1607354,"uid":61991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:43:50.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a6f0d86b3f40bc738dc9cac6b39f0f2a4ccac39f","tid":1607354,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:43:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"868e45d4de14348ecce590079212d51b5292d2e4","tid":1607354,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:44:25.000Z","msg":"總之可以正面宣傳就要做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f43d109d11a104f704071859f1c7b140f6db3c3","tid":1607354,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor